<pc>」</pc>乃伏罪<pc>。</pc>獻廟社<pc>，</pc>徇於市<pc>，</pc>斬於城西南獨柳下<pc>。</pc>子超郎等<measure quantity="9" unit="people">
<num value="9">九</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>與部將崔綱以次誅<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
